function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convAmbush, idActor, actorCultistSpeaker)
	
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_FXLOC_CHARGE, EG_CHARGE, true, Hydra.ACDID_INVALID, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(ID_SUMMONER_MAIN, ANIMKEY_OMNICHANNEL)
	
	-- Spawn the Succubus
	Hydra.ActorDelete(ID_FXLOC_CHARGE)
	Hydra.Wait(0.3)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(ID_SUMMONER_MAIN) then
		Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(ID_SUMMONER_MAIN, ANIMKEY_OMNICAST)
		Hydra.QActorSetIdleAnim(ID_SUMMONER_MAIN, ANIMKEY_NEUTRAL)
		Hydra.ActorSetTeam(ID_SUMMONER_MAIN, Hydra.TEAM_SCENERY)
		--Hydra.QActorEnableAI(ID_SUMMONER_MAIN, true)
	end
	Hydra.Wait(0.3)
	idSpawnedSuccubus = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(Hydra.ActorPickFromEncounter(ENCOUNTER_SUMMON, idSelf), ID_VICTIM_01, false, 0, 0, Hydra.MR_NORMAL, POWER_SPAWN)
	Hydra.ActorAddToGroup(idSpawnedSuccubus, "QST_Kehj_Caldeum_Cultist_Ambush")
	--Hydra.ActorSetTeam(idSpawnedSuccubus, Hydra.TEAM_SCENERY)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_FXLOC_BURST_01, EG_BURST)
	Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(ID_VICTIM_01, .2)
	Hydra.Wait(1.0)
	
	-- Spawn the fly demons
	idSpawnedFly01 = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(Hydra.ActorPickFromEncounter(ENCOUNTER_SUMMON_DEMONS, idSelf), ID_VICTIM_02, false, 0, 0, Hydra.MR_NORMAL, POWER_SPAWN)
	Hydra.ActorAddToGroup(idSpawnedFly01, "QST_Kehj_Caldeum_Cultist_Ambush")
	--Hydra.ActorSetTeam(idSpawnedFly, Hydra.TEAM_SCENERY)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_FXLOC_BURST_02, EG_BURST)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(ID_VICTIM_02, .2)
	
	idSpawnedFly02 = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(Hydra.ActorPickFromEncounter(ENCOUNTER_SUMMON_DEMONS, idSelf), ID_VICTIM_03, false, 0, 0, Hydra.MR_NORMAL, POWER_SPAWN)
	Hydra.ActorAddToGroup(idSpawnedFly02, "QST_Kehj_Caldeum_Cultist_Ambush")
	--Hydra.ActorSetTeam(idSpawnedFly, Hydra.TEAM_SCENERY)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_FXLOC_BURST_03, EG_BURST)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(ID_VICTIM_03, .2)
	
	Hydra.Wait(1.0)
	for i, Cultist in ipairs(tCultists) do
		Hydra.ActorClearAnimSetOverride(Cultist)
		Hydra.ActorSetTeam(Cultist, Hydra.TEAM_MONSTER_DEFAULT)
		Hydra.ActorSetNoDamage(Cultist, false)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(Cultist)
		Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	end		
	
end
